# Change Log

## [0.3.0] - 04/24/2015
### Added
- Add Shift+middle click shortcut.
- Add an option page for shortcuts setting.
- Add background color customerization.

### Updated
- Remove Alt+\<Key\> and Shift+Alt+\<Key\> due to shortcut conflict.
- Update the default action of Shift+\<Key\> from opening link in new window to new inactive tab.

## [0.2.5] - 04/22/2015
### Added
- Add more shortcuts including Shift+click, Ctrl+click, Ctrl+Shift+click, Alt+\<Key\> and Shift+Alt+\<Key\>.

### Fixed
- Update css files.